"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/643948","Department for International Development","false","2016-12-01","<p>I refer the hon. Member to the answer I provided on 7 November to Question numbers 51481 and 51482.</p>","Stockton South","James Wharton",,"2016-12-01T17:24:28.457Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/643948/answer","Biography information for James Wharton","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/643948/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/643948/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2016-11-24","Developing Countries: HIV Infection","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, what plans she has to undertake a stocktake review of her Department's work on HIV to assess its comparative performance with other countries (a) in general and (b) on Sustainable Development Goal 3.3.","false","Biography information for Caroline Lucas","Brighton, Pavilion","Caroline Lucas","54888"
